<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 06:19:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国对舍弗勒上半年收入构成压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-weighs-schaefflers-first-half-revenue-2024-08-06/</link><description>该集团周二表示，今年上半年，中国对德国机器和汽车零部件供应商舍弗勒公司的销售造成了压力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 06:05:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-weighs-schaefflers-first-half-revenue-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示，全球贸易好转提振中国七月出口扩大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-seen-expanded-july-lifted-by-global-trade-upturn-2024-08-06/</link><description>中国7月份的出口可能会以更快的速度攀升，因为制造商受益于全球商品贸易持续好转带来的订单增加，预计这将保持出口强劲并缓解关税恐慌。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 05:31:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-exports-seen-expanded-july-lifted-by-global-trade-upturn-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国公司在等待美国新的限制措施时囤积高端三星芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-firms-stockpile-high-end-samsung-chips-they-await-new-us-curbs-say-2024-08-06/</link><description>三名消息人士称，华为和百度等中国科技巨头以及初创公司正在囤积三星电子的高带宽内存（HBM）半导体，因为预计美国将限制向中国出口芯片。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 04:13:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-firms-stockpile-high-end-samsung-chips-they-await-new-us-curbs-say-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>台股暴跌后反弹，但涨幅迅速回落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-stocks-rebound-after-plunge-quickly-pare-gains-2024-08-06/</link><description>继前一天创纪录暴跌后，台湾股市周二上涨，但由于对美国经济和科技公司前景的持续担忧，上午晚些时候回吐了部分涨幅。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:19:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/taiwan-stocks-rebound-after-plunge-quickly-pare-gains-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对亚洲市场反弹的评论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-quotes-2024-08-06/</link><description>周二，亚洲股市从历史性抛售中反弹，美国央行行长试图缓解经济衰退担忧，日本领导人敦促保持冷静，日本股市大幅反弹，这支撑了亚洲股市。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:18:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-quotes-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>全球股市暴跌后中国股市难以反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-struggle-rebound-after-global-markets-slump-2024-08-06/</link><description>尽管地区市场出现反弹，但由于投资者仍担心中国经济复苏滞后，中国股市周二仍难以上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 03:14:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-stocks-struggle-rebound-after-global-markets-slump-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>套利交易的挤压让货币和投资者感到紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/squeeze-carry-trades-leave-currency-markets-edge-2024-08-06/</link><description>美元周二大幅下跌，日元在前一交易日大幅上涨后处于不利地位，因为交易员面临热门套利交易的平仓和美联储大幅降息的前景。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 01:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/squeeze-carry-trades-leave-currency-markets-edge-2024-08-06/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市在暴跌后寻求缓解反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-08-05/</link><description>亚洲股市周二有望出现缓解性反弹，因为期货显示遭受重创的日经指数将出现开盘反弹，而且央行官员也发表了所有正确的言论来安抚市场紧张情绪。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 23:25:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1pix-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：盘点日本历史性的市场崩盘</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-05/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 21:47:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>百胜中国宣布首席财务官辞职；肯德基、必胜客推动盈利增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/yum-brands-china-cfo-step-down-2024-08-05/</link><description>百胜中国周一表示，财务总监杨安迪 (Andy Yeung) 在担任该职位近五年后即将辞职，其季度盈利得益于肯德基和必胜客特许经营店的强劲业绩。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 20:47:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/yum-brands-china-cfo-step-down-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 称法院应拒绝司法部在剥离诉讼中提交的秘密文件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktok-says-court-should-reject-us-justice-secret-filings-divestiture-suit-2024-08-05/</link><description>TikTok 及其母公司字节跳动周一要求美国上诉法院驳回司法部秘密提起部分法律诉讼的请求，该诉讼捍卫了一项寻求在 1 月 19 日之前强制剥离 TikTok 美国资产或实施禁令的法律。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 19:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/tiktok-says-court-should-reject-us-justice-secret-filings-divestiture-suit-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>投资者对全球股市暴跌的评论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-selloff-quotes-6-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一，全球股市暴跌，债券上涨，原因是对美国可能陷入衰退的担忧导致投资者纷纷逃离风险资产，同时押注利率必须迅速下降才能挽救经济增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 15:12:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-selloff-quotes-6-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>恒大拟向创始人许志安及前高管追回60亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrandes-liquidators-obtain-injunctions-against-executives-2024-08-05/</link><description>中国恒大集团周一表示，其清算人正在寻求向包括创始人许家印在内的七名被告追回约60亿美元，并补充说他们已获得针对其中三人的禁令。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 12:55:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-evergrandes-liquidators-obtain-injunctions-against-executives-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国选手邹敬源卫冕双杠冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-chinas-zou-wins-mens-parallel-bars-gold-medal-2024-08-05/</link><description>周一，中国选手邹敬源轻松击败对手，卫冕奥运会双杠冠军，获得巴黎奥运会上的第三枚奖牌，为中国队赢得了体操项目的第二枚金牌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 10:35:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/gymnastics-chinas-zou-wins-mens-parallel-bars-gold-medal-2024-08-05/</guid></item><item><title>羽毛球单打决赛韩国选手安赛龙、丹麦选手安赛龙夺得金牌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-skoreas-an-beats-chinas-he-claim-womens-singles-gold-2024-08-05/</link><description>韩国选手安世英以21-13 21-16击败中国选手何冰娇，夺得羽毛球女单奥运金牌；丹麦选手安赛龙则以11-21 11-21击败泰国选手昆拉武特·维蒂萨恩，成功卫冕男子羽毛球项目冠军。 。</description><pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 09:58:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/badminton-skoreas-an-beats-chinas-he-claim-womens-singles-gold-2024-08-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>